Lesson 32 单词句型讲解

+ type          打字;类型;
    She is typing a letter.
    Is she typing a letter? Yes,she is.     No,she isn't.
    She isn't typing a letter?
    What is she doing?
    Who is typing a letter?(针对主语提问动词不需要提前，否则需要)

+ letter            信
+ love letter       情书
+ basket            篮子
+ basketball        篮球
+ eat               吃(咀嚼)
    eat breakfast/an apple/some brad
    eat soup        喝汤
    eat porridge    喝粥

+ take medicine     吃药
+ suck the breast   吃奶(小孩)
+ bone              骨头
+ clean             清洗
+ tooth             牙齿  teeth(复数)
+ cook              做饭；厨师
    I am cooking.   我正在做饭
+ cooker            炉子，餐具
+ milk              牛奶
+ meal              饭，一顿饭
+ drink             喝
    drink water/tea/coffee
+ have              有；喝；吃；
+ tap               (水)龙头
+ turn on tap       打开水龙头
+ turn off tap      关闭水龙头










